Package com.SuperheroSightings.springbootrestjdbctemplatemaven.dao

Interface OrganizationDAO

All Known Implementing Classes:
OrganizationDAOImpl
public interface OrganizationDAO
Interface for data access operations related to the Organization entity. This interface defines CRUD and other operations for the Organization entity.
